"volume for RAID</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>。)"

#. Tag: para
#: using-d-i.xml:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support for MD is a relatively new addition to the installer. You may "
"experience problems for some RAID levels and in combination with some "
